{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "青龙的水边 第2章 5-3 失去的象征",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "耶梦加得谈到了龙约。\\n龙约指的是人与龙之间的紧密联系。\\n而契约石，正是其代表性的产物。\\n据说最早的契约石“原始契约石”，\\n在300年前的一次纷争中丢失了。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "──逃跑途中",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "青龙……没想到会有\\n和曾经的同胞战斗的一天。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "耶梦加得……\\n你以前和青龙很要好吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "是的，我们曾经志同道合。\\n想不到如今要针锋相对。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "本不会相争之士，开始争斗，\\n本不可觉醒之物，即将觉醒……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "这个世界的理，\\n可能已经开始失控。\\n从“龙约之灾”发生那天开始。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "龙约之灾？\\n龙约是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "你想知道吗，王子？那么……\\n我就慢慢解开这个世界尘封的历史吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "龙约——\\n象征着龙与人之间的联系。比如……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "契约石也是其中之一。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "作为信赖的结晶，\\n有大有小，形态各不相同。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "其中最大的，\\n是距今一千年前出现的“原始契约石”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "一千年前，\\n原本敌对的人和龙达成和解，\\n立下了要相互尊敬的誓约。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "那时，便诞生了最初的契约石。\\n堪称是人龙关系蜜月期的象征。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "原始契约石由伊莉雅教会保管，\\n那结晶放出的光芒……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "融入到对龙心怀敬仰的英雄体内，\\n化为“龙之血”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "龙之血……原来如此，\\n接受那道光芒的就是我们王族的始祖吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那块原始契约石，\\n现在也是伊莉雅教会在保管吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "不，原始契约石\\n在距今大约三百年前……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "原始契约石在三百年前支离破碎了。\\n因为某场争端。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "并非因为\\n人与龙的关系不睦。\\n而是面对灾祸，迫不得已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "那正是“龙约之灾”。\\n失去契约石之后，\\n一时间并未产生什么影响……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "但三百年后……\\n流着龙之血的王族之间、以及龙之间，\\n开始了争斗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "从表面上看，只是单纯的争斗。\\n但是从深层次来看……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "一切都是以失去了象征为契机，\\n世界开始扭曲。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "“龙约之灾”……\\n人和龙之间的誓约不复存在……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不过，我们和龙之间的信赖关系\\n并没有完全消失！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我也和你缔结了契约。\\n将来，\\n一定会有那么一天……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "嗯，即使原始契约石碎裂，\\n也不代表我们的誓约就此终结。\\n而且……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "原始的光辉也不会消逝。\\n晨曦的微光\\n依旧在深夜中摇曳。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "但要重现真正的龙约，\\n还需要漫长的岁月。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "渐渐加深彼此的信赖，\\n最终才能化为结晶。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那究竟\\n需要多少时间？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "这就看你的了，尤蒂尔。\\n一切都取决于\\n信任龙之人的行动……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "耶梦加得",
            "context": "我们正在接受试炼。\\n即便誓约一度消失，\\n是否……仍能经得起时间的考验。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "喂，快把他们找出来！\\n这是艾缪尔大人的命令！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "快走吧，耶梦加得。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我希望你能见证，\\n我们是如何面对这场考验的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_09_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}